"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미셸","body":"아~아. 「하구미」라고 자기 입으로 말했잖아.\n하지만…… 그랬지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"m_nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event40-06-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":217}],"windowDisplayName":"마리","body":"미셸……?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":217,"motionName":"m_nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":217,"voiceId":"event40-06-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미셸","body":"영……차, 나는 이제 빠르게 뛸 자신은 없지만\n반드시 골인할게. 걸어서라도.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"m_nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event40-06-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":217}],"windowDisplayName":"마리","body":"……! 응! 미셸, 같이 골까지 가자!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":217,"motionName":"m_nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":217,"voiceId":"event40-06-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미셸","body":"아니야. 마리는 제대로 뛰어서 가. 나는 신경 쓰지 말고.\n그것이 「정정당당한 진지한 대결」일 것 같아.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"m_nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event40-06-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":217}],"windowDisplayName":"마리","body":"그렇구나……! 그렇지!\n하구미, 열심히 할게! 미셸도 열심히 해!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":217,"motionName":"m_nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":217,"voiceId":"event40-06-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미셸","body":"아하하…… 힘내, 하구미.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"m_nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event40-06-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"앗……! 미셸이랑 마리가 다시 뛰기 시작했구나!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event40-06-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId"